"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931713-henry-fieldman-olympics-rowing-medal-team-gb\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GB star Henry Fieldman has become the first person to ever win anOlympicmedal in both men and women's events.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henry Fieldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Fieldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fieldman claimed his second bronze medal at the Paris 2024 Games on Saturday as Team GB came third in the women's eight rowing.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999925635166, \"rank\": 7.170474745076503e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He etches his name into the history books, having already won bronze in the men's eight at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8691515084518895, \"rank\": 0.15054682012195056, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old was able to achieve the extraordinary feat thanks to his unique role as a coxswain in rowing.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coxswains are allowed to be included in a team with rowers of the opposite sex following a rule change in 2017.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their primary role is to be in charge of guiding the boat - sitting at the stern, steering, calling the stroke and generally implementing the strategy of races.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB finished with a time of 5:59.51, finishing behind runners-up Canada and gold medallists Romania.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999925635166, \"rank\": 7.170474745076503e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9630482073076732, \"rank\": 0.03577652806641893, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fieldman stated following the triumph that he hopes the bronze medal will lead to the women's eight becoming regular medallists at future global events.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope that now that we have had two Olympic medals in the women's eight that this could be the start of more women's eights medals to come - stepping on to greater things,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team's rowers were: Heidi Long, Rowan McKellar, Holly Dunford, Emily Ford, Lauren Irwin, Eve Stewart, Harriet Taylor and Annie Campbell-Orde.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"score\": 0.9867136309779886, \"rank\": 0.01346488132400749, \"text\": \"Heidi\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heidi\"}, {\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"score\": 0.8317935624458187, \"rank\": 0.1887259186128855, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buddy_Holly\"}, {\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Dunford\", \"score\": 0.9999995762524111, \"rank\": 4.2034720410885697e-07, \"text\": \"Dunford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Dunford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Dunford\"}, {\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999999999677129, \"rank\": 3.2291870340831505e-11, \"text\": \"Emily Ford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\", \"score\": 0.9998895981886788, \"rank\": 0.00011027302839562031, \"text\": \"Irwin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Irwin\"}, {\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eve Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eve_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"score\": 0.9382427582734828, \"rank\": 0.06577471116782986, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Brackett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere, Great Britain defied the odds by winning gold in the men's eight.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8681611044509746, \"rank\": 0.15185315498165539, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British boat traded the lead with the Netherlands before surging ahead in the third quarter of the 2,000m race, and won by 1.08 seconds after clocking in a time of 5:22.8.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8570227106307333, \"rank\": 0.1622360257021302, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.999344699234214, \"rank\": 0.00047143754729286116, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999447482, \"rank\": 5.524718200588076e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9943757716000412, \"rank\": 0.005656038718441739, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fieldman's success in both male and female events follows heated debate over the inclusion of transgender athletes at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Algerian boxer Imane Khelif - who was born female and has never identified as male - has been inaccurately described as transgender by various public figures such J.K. Rowling and Donald Trump.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 1998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9982080475652623, \"rank\": 0.0017534618979731203, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0663549166304433e-18, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999837114047, \"rank\": 1.627987387464333e-08, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy came when she defeated Italian boxer Angela Carini, who abandoned their bout inside 46 seconds and failed to shake the Algerian's hand.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2224, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.8422502976073142, \"rank\": 0.18304195036512713, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2320, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9982080475652623, \"rank\": 0.0017534618979731203, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was heard repeatedly saying \\\"it's not right,\\\" and commented afterwards: \\\"I have never been hit with such a powerful punch.\\\"\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Khelif last year was disqualified from the women's World Championships in New Delhi for failing a gender eligibility test - the contents of which remain unknown.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999666717632559, \"rank\": 3.332722535201262e-05, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not specified why the now-banned and Russia-led International Boxing Association (IBA), which carried out the supposed tests, said Khelif \\\"failed to meet the eligibility criteria for participating in the women's competition\\\".\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2927, \"end\": 2959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.073205914752274e-23, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9625092438272771, \"rank\": 0.03895105563314089, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympics Committee addressed the IBA's murky tests this week, saying: \\\"This is not a transgender issue.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympics Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9625092438272771, \"rank\": 0.03895105563314089, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These women have been competing in competitions for many years.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The testosterone is not a perfect test.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many women can have elevated levels of testosterone, which is in what would be called 'male levels' and still be women and still compete as women.\\\"\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3618, \"end\": 3631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.454842843328516e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3667, \"end\": 3680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.454842843328516e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"